    "markdown-readme":  "# Upscale Video (SeedVR2)\n\nVideo upscaling pipeline built on SeedVR2 and VHS video IO.\n\n## Inputs\n- **video**: Video handle/path.\n- **model**: String. SeedVR2 model name.\n- **new_resolution**: Integer. Target height/width depending on node.\n- **preserve_vram**: Boolean. Memory-optimized path.\n- **seed / batch_size**: Generation controls.\n- **VHS_LoadVideo**: Optional frame rate/size overrides.\n\n## Outputs\n- **image-0 / images**: Frames for preview/processing.\n- Saved frames/video via Save nodes (configure prefixes/paths).\n\n## Tips\nUse the comparison display node to visually inspect improvements frame-by-frame.",
